Live Nation Entertainment Inc. (LYV)  said
it signed an amended contract with President and Chief Executive
Officer Michael Rapino extending his tenure with the worldâ€™s
biggest concert promoter and ticket seller through 2017.  The existing accord with Rapino, 47, was scheduled to
expire on May 31, 2014, according to a regulatory filing today.
Rapino will receive $2.3 million in annual base pay starting
Jan. 1, 2013. He was granted options for 3.6 million shares at
